===Etymology===
From Old French ''[[particuler]]'', from Latin ''[[particularis]]''.  See [[particle]].

===Adjective===
'''particular'''
#[[specific]]; [[discrete]]; a part or portion of something.
#Concerned with, or attentive to, [[detail]]s; [[minute]]; [[precise]]; [[fastidious]].

